parameters.jsCode:
const body = $input.item.json.body;
return {
  json: {
    dos_file: body.dos_file || null,
    lessons_learned_file: body.lessons_learned_file || null,
    pjb_template_file: body.pjb_template_file || null,
    well_name: body.well_name || '',
    well_number: body.well_number || '',
    zob_number: body.zob_number || '',
    rig_name: body.rig_name || '',
    date: body.date || new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-GB'),
    customer: body.customer || ''
  }
};

parameters.text:
=Analyze this DOS PowerPoint.

TASK 1: Find slide numbers for:
- Well Objective
- BHA Overview
- DAP
- Value Moment
- Well Details
- Mandatory Routine
- Contact List

TASK 2: Find current values that need replacing:
- Look for well names (e.g., "West Linus A-12H")
- Look for rig names (e.g., "Deepsea Bergen")
- Look for dates
- Look for well numbers
- Look for ZOB numbers

New values to use:
Well: {{ $json.well_name }}
Well#: {{ $json.well_number }}
ZOB: {{ $json.zob_number }}
Rig: {{ $json.rig_name }}
Date: {{ $json.date }}

Return JSON:
{
  "slides": {
    "well_objective": [1, 2],
    "bha_overview": [3],
    "dap": [4, 5]
  },
  "replacements": [
    {"old": "West Linus A-12H", "new": "{{ $json.well_name }}"},
    {"old": "Deepsea Bergen", "new": "{{ $json.rig_name }}"}
  ]
}
